        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1367",
        "content": "Earl March look'd on his dying child, And smit with grief to view her- The youth, he cried, whom I exiled Shall be restored to woo her.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
