        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1367",
        "content": "The moving waters at their priestlike task Of pure ablution round earth's human shores, Or gazing on the new soft fallen mask Of snow upon the mountains and the moors:--",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
