        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1367",
        "content": "When I behold, upon the night's starr'd face, Huge cloudy symbols of a high romance, And think that I may never live to trace Their shadows, with the magic hand of chance;",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
