        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1367",
        "content": "Surprized by joy-impatient as the wind- I turn'd to share the transport-Oh, with whom But Thee-deep buried in the silent tomb, That spot which no vicissitude can find?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
