        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1367/291967/1367_291967_000037_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1367",
        "content": "Knowing my heart's best treasure was no more; That neither present time, nor years unborn Could to my sight that heavenly face restore.",
