        "content": "Now joy, old England, raise! For the tidings of thy might, By the festal cities' blaze, Whilst the wine cup shines in light; And yet amidst that joy and uproar, Let us think of them that sleep Full many a fathom deep By thy wild and stormy steep, Elsinore!",
